Summary: This section details the properties of the VisualInstance3D class, including layers, sorting offset, and sorting use of AABB center.

Properties
* layers (int): The rendering layers the instance belongs to. Default: 1
* sorting_offset (float): The offset used for sorting transparent objects. Default: 0.0
* sorting_use_aabb_center (bool): Determines if the center of the AABB should be used for sorting.
