Document: VisualInstance3D
Path: godot/classes/class_visualinstance3d.rst
Summary: Provides methods for accessing and manipulating the bounding box, base RID, and layer mask values of a 3D visual instance.

Methods
* _get_aabb() → AABB: virtual, const. Returns the AABB of the visual instance.
* get_aabb() → AABB: const. Returns the AABB of the visual instance.
* get_base() → RID: const. Returns the base RID of the visual instance.
* get_instance() → RID: const. Returns the instance RID of the visual instance.
* get_layer_mask_value(layer_number: int) → bool: const. Returns whether the specified layer mask bit is set.
* set_base(base: RID): Sets the base RID of the visual instance.
* set_layer_mask_value(layer_number: int, value: bool): Sets the specified layer mask bit.
